WEBVTT

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:31.360
changed my perception
about menstruation forever.

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:37.736
In 2009, Tuhin and I were pursuing
our postgraduation in design.

00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:39.416
We fell in love with each other

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:41.880
and I was at ease
discussing periods with him.

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:44.560
Tuhin knew little about periods.

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.800
(Laughter)

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:55.416
He was astonished to know
that girls get painful cramps

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:56.856
and we bleed every month.

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:58.976
(Laughter)

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:00.496
Yeah.